## 🤖 RAG Development Rules

### Embedding Consistency (CRITICAL ⚠️)
- **ALWAYS use the same embedding model for documents and queries**
- Current standard: OpenAI text-embedding-3-small (1536 dimensions)
- Document processing uses OpenAI (NO fallback to different models)
- Query processing MUST also use OpenAI (dimension mismatch = zero results)
- Different models have different dimensions and are incompatible

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - consistent model
const docEmbedding = await openaiClient.generateEmbedding({
  text: documentChunk,
  model: "text-embedding-3-small"
});

const queryEmbedding = await openaiClient.generateEmbedding({
  text: userQuery,
  model: "text-embedding-3-small"  // MUST match
});

// ❌ Wrong - dimension mismatch
const docEmbedding = await openaiClient.generateEmbedding(text);  // 1536 dims
const queryEmbedding = await embeddingClient.generateHuggingFaceEmbedding(query);  // 4096 dims
// Result: Zero search results
```

### Text Chunking Best Practices
- **Standard configuration**: 800 tokens per chunk, 100 token overlap
- **Preserve sentence boundaries**: Split on periods to maintain semantic coherence
- **Include page metadata**: Track page numbers for citations
- **Maintain source attribution**: Required for RAG citation accuracy

```typescript
const textChunks = chunkPages(pageContents, {
  maxChunkSize: 800,         // Balances context vs. precision
  overlap: 100,              // Prevents info loss at boundaries
  preserveSentences: true    // Maintains semantic coherence
});
```

### Qdrant Collection Strategy
- **Per-project isolation**: `insightsphere_user_{userId}_project_{projectId}`
- **Lazy creation**: Create collection on first document upload
- **Vector config**: size=1536 (OpenAI), distance=Cosine
- **Rich metadata**: documentId, projectId, userId, fileName, pageNumber, chunkIndex, createdAt

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - per-project collection with metadata
await qdrantService.upsertChunks(documentChunks, {
  useProjectCollection: true  // Required
});

// ❌ Wrong - missing project isolation
await qdrantService.upsertChunks(documentChunks);
```

### RAG Query Optimization
- **Use filters for security**: ALWAYS filter by projectId + userId
- **Similarity threshold**: 0.7 minimum for relevance
- **Limit results**: 10 chunks max for context (fits in 4K token window)
- **Build context with citations**: Include source metadata for transparency

```typescript
const results = await qdrantService.searchSimilar(queryVector, {
  userId: user.id,              // Required for collection selection
  projectId: project.id,        // Required for filtering
  useProjectCollection: true,   // Required
  threshold: 0.7,               // Minimum relevance
  limit: 10                     // Max chunks
});
```

