## 📊 Qdrant Best Practices

### Collection Management
- **Lazy creation**: Create collections only when first document uploaded
- **Delete collections when projects deleted**: Clean up user data
- **Check collection exists before search**: Prevent errors
- **Handle dimension mismatches**: Recreate collection if dimensions change

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - ensure collection exists
const collectionName = await qdrantService.ensureCollection(
  userId,
  1536,  // Embedding dimensions
  projectId
);

// ✅ Clean up on project deletion
await qdrantService.deleteUserData(userId);
```

### Metadata Schema
**Required fields** (MUST include in every chunk):
- `documentId`: UUID of source document
- `projectId`: UUID of project (for filtering)
- `userId`: UUID of owner (for collection selection)
- `fileName`: Original filename (for citations)
- `fileType`: pdf, docx, etc.
- `createdAt`: ISO timestamp

**Optional fields** (include when available):
- `pageNumber`: Page number in document (for citations)
- `chunkIndex`: Index within document (for ordering)
- `summary`: Brief chunk summary (future feature)
- `embeddingModel`: Model used (for debugging)

```typescript
// ✅ Complete metadata
const chunk: DocumentChunk = {
  id: createChunkId(documentId, index, pageNumber),
  content: chunkText,
  embedding: embeddingVector,
  metadata: {
    documentId,
    projectId,
    userId,
    fileName: "research.pdf",
    fileType: "pdf",
    pageNumber: 5,
    chunkIndex: index,
    createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),
    embeddingModel: "text-embedding-3-small"
  }
};
```

### Search Patterns
- **Always include security filters**: userId (collection), projectId (filtering)
- **Use appropriate thresholds**: 0.7 for relevance, 0.8+ for high precision
- **Limit results**: Prevent context overflow (10 chunks ≈ 8000 tokens)
- **Extract metadata for citations**: fileName, pageNumber for source attribution

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - secure filtered search
const results = await qdrantService.searchSimilar(queryVector, {
  userId: user.id,                 // Required
  projectId: currentProject.id,    // Filter to project
  useProjectCollection: true,      // Use project collection
  threshold: 0.7,                  // Minimum similarity
  limit: 10                        // Max results
});

// ❌ Wrong - no security filtering
const results = await qdrantService.searchSimilar(queryVector, {
  limit: 100  // Too many results, no access control
});
```

### Performance Optimization
- **Batch upsert for multiple chunks**: 100 chunks at a time
- **Connection pooling**: Reuse Qdrant client (singleton pattern)
- **Avoid full collection scans**: Always use filters
- **Index optimization**: Use Cosine distance for embeddings

```typescript
// ✅ Batch upsert (efficient)
const BATCH_SIZE = 100;
for (let i = 0; i < allChunks.length; i += BATCH_SIZE) {
  const batch = allChunks.slice(i, i + BATCH_SIZE);
  await qdrantService.upsertChunks(batch, { useProjectCollection: true });
}

// ❌ Individual upserts (slow)
for (const chunk of allChunks) {
  await qdrantService.upsertChunks([chunk], { useProjectCollection: true });
}
```

